PrecisAuthority to enter into the CANADA-BRITISH COLUMBIA AGREEMENT ON A BUSINESS SERVICE CENTRE which provides for the establishment of a Business Service Centre in Vancouver to support business development and the entrepreneurial process by providing one-stop shopping for accurate, speedy and user- friendly information and data required for sound business decision-making, including advice on government programs and services.
